{
  "stem": "1502.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That letter was good enough to be postponed, to skip one transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We got that letter a few days before the transport, and that's what gave us the chance to be what they called [NON-ENGLISH], postponed for the next transport.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember Mayer, the Jewish kapo, came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Before the transport, he went into each hold with a list of the people that have postponed for the next transport.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was looking out the window, I remember, to see if Mayer is coming towards the quarters of the [? flitzers, ?] of the escapees.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Each hall had what they called a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was-- he was-- the head of the-- he was running the-- the hall.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He was the-- he was the leader, he was the chief.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I remember my [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "His name was Gingold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We had very few people in our hall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There were only maybe six or seven.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he himself was not an escapee.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He was there from the beginning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He was there because he was married to a non-Jewish-- his wife was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And she somehow worked for him that he should stay in the camp, he shouldn't be deported.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He was an elderly man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He saw me looking at-- at courtyard if Mayer is coming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He told me, listen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I don't want you to be disappointed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But I'm here for two years in this escapee.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I'm the leader of this room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I want you to know that it never happened that a [? flitzer, ?] an escape, should skip a transport, should be put for-- for a-- for another transport.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "That doesn't exist.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So make-- don't make yourself any illusions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "You'll be deported.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Mayer did not come to our room, to the escapee room, he didn't come because it was an impossibility.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
